<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Star system</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,300,700|Raleway:300,400,500,700">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">

    <!-- HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!-- Leave those next 4 lines if you care about users using IE8 -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="banner" style="background: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('images/back.jpg');">
      <div class="banner-content">
        <h1>Prêt pour la vie de rêve ?</h1>
        <p>Partez à la rencontre des stars célibataires du show-biz et vivez une expérience inoubliable !</p>
        <form action="#" class="form-inline">
          <input type="text" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Date d'arrivée">
          <input type="text" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Date de départ">
          <select name="" id="" class="form-control input-lg">
            <option value="1">1 beauf</option>
            <option value="2">2 beaufs</option>
            <option value="3">3 beaufs</option>
            <option value="4">Une famille de chtis</option>
          </select>
          <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" value="Rejoins les stars !">
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container text-center padded features">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
          <img src="images/globe.png" alt="">
          <h2>Découvrez le monde</h2>
          <p>Nos stars vivent partout dans le monde.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
          <%= image_tag "dollar.png", class: "img-rounded avatar" %>
          <h2>Payez directement en cash</h2>
          <p>L'escort de luxe n'a jamais été aussi facile.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
          <img src="images/beer.png" alt="">
          <h2>Buvez comme des trous</h2>
          <p>Ne soyez jamais à court de boisson.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
          <img src="images/heart.png" alt="">
          <h2>Trouvez l'amour</h2>
          <p>Rejoignez une communauté de penseurs libres.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
<h1 class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 50px">Rencontre des célibataires non consanguins !</h1>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <% data.flats.each do |owner, flat| %>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
      <div class="card" style="background: url('<%= image_path flat.picture %>'), linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%= image_path flat.picture %>');">
        <div class="card-category"><%= flat.city %></div>
        <div class="card-description">
          <h2><%= flat.name %></h2>
          <p><%= flat.summary %></p>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag flat.owner_picture, class:"card-user avatar avatar-large" %>
        <%= link_to "#", "flats/#{owner}.html", class: "card-link" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>


    <div class="text-center padded" id="newsletter">
      <h2>Get news from us</h2>
      <p>Leave us your mail and get news from us</p>
      <form class="form-inline">
        <input type="email" placeholder="bob@gmail.com" class="form-control">
        <input type="submit" value="Subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">
      </form>
    </div>



    <!-- Including Bootstrap JS (with its jQuery dependency) so that dynamic components work -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>

